## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of recent data and the potential bias in opinion-based sources. While surveys provide quantitative insights, they may not capture the full complexity of individual beliefs. Additionally, the reliance on English-language sources may exclude perspectives from non-English speaking regions or communities. Further research could benefit from a broader range of sources and more recent data to capture evolving public opinions.